name: High Wheeler
description:
The apocalypse has reached a lovely fantasy town. Everyone is gone while you try to escape the city with your Bike (its a Penny farthing). Sadly you can barely balance yourself.

This game is just a quick attempt to fit the theme Unstable and it's made in 3 days. I sadly did not get HTML5 export to work, as there seems to be an issue with HTML5 and Godot Beta 1.

Controls
A/D or Arrows Keys to balance yourself
